and variance operators.

00:35:02.680 --> 00:35:06.430
Variance operators will square
coefficients in front of them.

00:35:06.430 --> 00:35:12.770
Covariance operators will
bring the coefficient outside.

00:35:12.770 --> 00:35:15.790
